sequenceDiagram
    participant S as Seller
    participant D as DALP
    participant B as Buyer
    S->>D: Initiate settlement leg
    B->>D: Confirm payment leg
    D->>D: Validate both legs
    alt Both legs valid
        D->>S: Execute asset transfer
        D->>B: Execute payment transfer
        D->>S: Confirm finality
        D->>B: Confirm finality
    else Either leg fails
        D->>S: Reject: settlement cancelled
        D->>B: Reject: settlement cancelled
    end
